      <title>黑客袭击了加密行业安全领域最知名的人物之一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/hacker-hits-one-of-crypto-industry-s-biggest-names-in-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最新的加密货币黑客攻击涉及业界安全领域的顶级品牌之一：硬件钱包制造商 Ledger。这家总部位于巴黎的初创公司周四早些时候发现其 Ledger Connect Kit 软件遭到泄露，导致数十万美元从用户钱包中流失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/hacker-hits-one-of-crypto-industry-s-biggest-names-in-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 20:49:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
